## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- [Rust](https://rustup.rs/) 1.81+
- [Just](https://github.com/casey/just) (optional, for convenience)

### Installation

```bash
# Install Rust
curl --proto '=https' --tlsv1.2 -sSf https://sh.rustup.rs | sh

# Install Just (optional)
cargo install just
```

## Commands

### Build

```bash
just build              # Build all components
cargo build            # Alternative using cargo directly
{% if cli_module == 'enabled' and 'rust' in cli_languages %}
just build-cli         # Build CLI only
{% endif %}
{% if api_module == 'enabled' and 'rust' in api_languages %}
just build-api         # Build API server only
{% endif %}
```

{% if cli_module == 'enabled' and 'rust' in cli_languages %}
### CLI Usage

```bash
# Run the CLI
just run-cli hello World

# Or directly with cargo
cargo run --bin {{ package_name }} -- hello World

# Get help
just run-cli --help

# Check version
just run-cli version
```

#### Available Commands

- `hello` - Say hello to someone
- `version` - Display version information
{% endif %}

{% if api_module == 'enabled' and 'rust' in api_languages %}
### API Server

```bash
# Run in development mode
just run-api-dev

# Or start normally
just run-api

# Or with cargo
cargo run --bin {{ package_name }}-api
```

#### Environment Variables

- `HOST` - Server host (default: `0.0.0.0`)
- `PORT` - Server port (default: `8080`)
- `ENVIRONMENT` - Environment mode (`development`, `production`)
- `CORS_ENABLED` - Enable CORS (default: `true`)
- `LOG_LEVEL` - Logging level (default: `info`)

#### API Endpoints

- `GET /health` - Health check endpoint
- `GET /ready` - Readiness probe
- `GET /live` - Liveness probe
- `GET /api/v1/hello?name=NAME` - Hello endpoint
{% endif %}

### Testing

```bash
just test              # Run all tests
just test-verbose      # Run tests with output
cargo test             # Alternative using cargo
```

### Quality Checks

```bash
just quality           # Run all quality checks (fmt + clippy + test)
just fmt               # Format code
just fmt-check         # Check formatting without changes
just clippy            # Run clippy linter
just clippy-all        # Run clippy with all features
```

### Maintenance

```bash
just clean             # Clean build artifacts
just update            # Update dependencies
just outdated          # Check for outdated dependencies
just audit             # Run security audit
```

